data.description: GORGEOUS 4 BEDROOM, 4 BATHROOM TOWNHOME IN THE DESIRABLE STROH RANCH COMMUNITY!! The minute you walk in you will fall IN LOVE with the bright and sunny open floor plan with vaulted ceilings!! Beautiful kitchen with plenty of cabinet and counter space. Newly painted cabinets with custom hardware! Newer refrigerator. Spacious dining area that opens up to the cozy family room with a beautiful gas fireplace featuring custom stone and a hand built mantel!! Main floor bedroom or office conveniently located next to the laundry area and main floor bathroom with walk-in shower making this the perfect layout for an in-law suite!! Upstairs features 2 additional bedrooms including a master suite with 5 piece master bathroom and HUGE walk in closet!! Additional full bathroom next to the secondary bedroom. You'll love the partially finished basement which features another bedroom or family room with a custom built fireplace perfect for those snowy nights! Two closets and a bathroom with a walk in shower!! Additional storage space in the basement. Enjoy your morning coffee or evening beverage on your private ground level deck with pergola surrounded by beautiful trees and flowers!! Covered front porch!! OVERSIZED 2 car garage!  This home is a PERFECT location and has 3 guest parking spots right in front of the unit making it easy for your guests to park and walk right in!! Brand new carpet and interior paint! New laminate wood floors on the main level. Douglas County Schools, community clubhouse, sparkling pool, fitness center, tennis courts and trails. Close proximity to Stroh Ranch Soccer Fields, Meridian Golf Club, Parker Fieldhouse, Double Angel Baseball Fields as well as several other area parks for outdoor adventure! Easy access to 470/I-25 and only 15 minutes to Park Meadows Mall. This one won't last! Don't miss out on owning one of BEST townhomes loved and cared for by the original owners!! IMMACULATE condition!! AMAZING floor plan and LOCATION!
